    <!-- Vulnerabilities Section -->
    <div class="news-item">
        <h2>🔥 Vulnerabilities</h2>

        <p>⚠️ <b>Microsoft Patches Zero-Day Exploited in BYOVD Attacks</b><br>
        Microsoft has discovered **five vulnerabilities** in the **Paragon Partition Manager BioNTdrv.sys** driver, including **CVE-2025-0289**, exploited in **zero-day ransomware attacks**.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/ransomware-gangs-exploit-paragon-partition-manager-bug-in-byovd-attacks/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

        <p>🔴 <b>Cellebrite Zero-Day Exploited to Unlock Android Phones</b><br>
        Serbian authorities allegedly used **Cellebrite’s mobile forensic tools** to exploit **Linux USB driver flaws** in Android devices.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/serbian-police-used-cellebrite-zero-day-hack-to-unlock-android-phones/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

        <p>📡 <b>Bluetooth Security Risks: Eavesdropping & MITM Attacks</b><br>
        Tarlogic researchers highlight **Bluetooth vulnerabilities** that allow attackers to **intercept calls, steal data, and manipulate connections**.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://www.itsecurityguru.org/2025/02/28/tarlogic-discovers-security-flaw-allowing-eavesdropping-on-private-conversations-via-bluetooth-headset-microphone/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Adversaries Section -->
    <div class="news-item">
        <h2>🕵️ Adversaries & Attacks</h2>

        <p>🚨 <b>Qilin Ransomware Claims Attack on Lee Enterprises</b><br>
        The **Qilin ransomware gang** has **leaked samples** of allegedly stolen **350GB of sensitive data** from **Lee Enterprises**.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/qilin-ransomware-claims-attack-at-lee-enterprises-leaks-stolen-data/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

        <p>🛑 <b>Microsoft Exposes Storm-2139 Cybercriminals Behind AI Abuse</b><br>
        Four cybercriminals exploited **Azure AI services** to **generate illicit content**, including **deepfake celebrity images**.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://securityaffairs.com/174779/cyber-crime/azure-abuse-scheme-individuals-exposed.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
