        <h2>📈 Cybersecurity Trends</h2>

        <p>🔹 <b>Crypto Scammers Target AI Trading Bots with Fake Smart Contracts</b><br>
        Following the **LIBRA scam**, fraudsters are now deploying **fake tokens with backdoors** to manipulate **AI trading bots**.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://www.cysecurity.news/2025/03/crypto-scammers-are-targeting-ai-trade.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

        <p>🛑 <b>5,000+ Phishing PDFs Spreading Lumma Stealer Malware</b><br>
        Attackers use **fake CAPTCHA images** in **PDFs hosted on Webflow’s CDN** to infect victims with **Lumma Stealer malware**.</p>
        <p>🔗 <a href="https://thehackernews.com/2025/02/5000-phishing-pdfs-on-260-domains.html" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
